"As a participant, I need the forms to be presented in a way suitable for those with accessibility needs 
including colour scheme, font size and colour contrast, so that it is easy to read for all people."
Label: Deliver Last (Low Risk/Low Value)
Moscow: Should
Story Points: 5

Background:  All pages that the participants can see should abide by WCAG principles, with regards
to size, colour contrast, and Font.  
https://www.w3.org/WAI/standards-guidelines/wcag/

"Please use a modern readable typeface. Something like Montserrat or Poppins. 
I'm a little obsessed with good use of typography."
